    "en": {
      "title": "Lanka IOC Tankers to report to work",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); All fuel transport vehicles of Lanka IOC have been informed to report into service.",
        "The Chairman of the Lanka IOC Tanker Owners\u2019 Association Kusum Sadanayake said that at present between 75 and 100 vehicles are being operated daily, and IOC owns about 160 tanks.",
        "Meanwhile, the General Secretary of the Petroleum Private Tanker Owners\u2019 Association Shantha Silva said that NO fuel transport vehicles will travel to the Ceypetco filling stations on Thursday (30).",
        "IMF Staff Concludes Visit to Sri Lanka; discussions will continue towards reaching a staff-level agreement"
      ],
